platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: We love how AllTrails helps you zero in on just what you’re looking for. Filter search results by difficulty level and elevation gain, or find trails with waterfalls or hot springs—or that are dog-friendly. Reviews and photos submitted by the AllTrails community give you a full picture (and often insider details) before you head out.
按難度、海拔高度等搜尋行山路線，甚至能夠找到適合與狗狗同行的路線。此外，你可透過社群評論，在出發前更全面地了解路線的情況。
Search trails by difficulty level, elevation gain and more – even find ones that are dog-friendly. Plus, community reviews will give you a bigger picture before you head out.

Recherchez des sentiers par niveau de difficulté, dénivelé et autres (trouvez-en même qui sont adaptés aux chiens). Les commentaires de la communauté vous donneront une idée plus précise du terrain avant de partir.
有了這款 App，你就能根據步道的難度、爬升，甚至是否適合帶狗等條件，搜尋理想的路線。更棒的是，社群評價還能幫助你在出發前做好萬全準備。
